articles.title: **About this site**
articles.contents:
About me
My name is Farhan Sadeek. I am a sophomore in Dublin Coffman High
School in Columbus, Ohio. I love Data Science and am interested to dive
deep into this field.
About this project
My project includes the correlation between different countries and
economics.
Goals
Visualize distribution of donations from countries over time
Examine change of US government representation along with donation
amount over time
x axis are different scales, so must convert to percentage before
facet-wrapping

Determine connection between foreign-connected PAC donations of
different parties and US government representation of the parties
“This is Data Science”

Preceptor

Kane’s Free High School
Data Science Bootcamp
